## Proposed Changes

### Feature 1: Retreat → ActivateSkill

Replace action slot 6 from a duplicate navigation action to **ActivateSkill** — triggers the game profile's `activate_buff` on the brain faction. The coordinate parameter is **ignored** (non-spatial action).

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Rust `ActivateBuff` directive already exists and is fully functional ([executor.rs:L77-109](file:///Users/manifera/Documents/GitHub/mass-swarm-ai-simulator/micro-core/src/systems/directive_executor/executor.rs#L77-L109)). The buff system supports cooldowns, modifiers, and entity targeting. **Zero Rust changes needed.**

