## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **ECP formula design**: For the current curriculum, should ECP simply be `stat[0]` (HP) for all stages, or do we want Stage 7+ (heterogeneous units) to use a multi-stat formula like `HP × (1 + armor)`? The infrastructure supports any product of stat indices. Using plain HP keeps things simpler initially while still fixing the pipeline.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **ActivateSkill unlock stage**: The current profile unlocks it at Stage 6. Should we move it earlier (e.g., Stage 1 where the debuff mechanic already uses `ActivateBuff`), or keep Stage 6 as the introduction point?

